comment:
not supported by evidence; disialylated Gal found on GlcNAcT4 arm
G60929YB,N-glycan_a-D-Manp_4,N4,Man,a,D,p,NC,6,Manp,14,,,validated by Qrator,,PMID: 25165152

GNT6 only makes penta-antennary; i.e. requires previous GlcNAc addition to 6-position of 6-linked Man (by GNT5).  Activity not yet detected in mammals.  Activity reported in chicken oviduct.  But even in chicken the triantennary glycan (4-substitution without 6-substititutioni) is not allowed
